## Project

Code and Pipeline is on [GitHub](https://github.com/ptr727/ESPHome-NonRoot).  
Docker images are published on [Docker Hub](https://hub.docker.com/r/ptr727/esphome-nonroot).  
Images are updated weekly with the latest upstream updates.

## Docker Builds and Tags

- `latest` : Latest `main` branch version.
- `develop` : Latest `develop` branch version.
- [version] : ESPHome version number.

## Platform Support

- `linux/amd64`
- `linux/arm64`

